######################################################################
#### @application screen
#### @type config-file
####

#### Clear/Refresh background color of screen
####   - The trouble isn't that background doesn't work, but rather 
####   that when opening a program with screen, the background doesn't
####   change over whitespace. For instance, as I type this, each 
####   changed char background color is black background (set by vim),
####   but unchanged white space is blue (set bg color of shell).
defbce "on"

#### Set mouse scrolling on by default
termcapinfo xterm* ti@:te@
